<h2>Hello <%= @employee.name %>,</h2>

<p>Your shift assignment has been confirmed:</p>

<div style="background-color: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
  <p><strong>Department:</strong> <%= @shift.department.name %></p>
  <p><strong>Shift Type:</strong> <%= @shift.shift_type.titleize %></p>
  <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @shift.start_time.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
  <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= @shift.start_time.strftime('%I:%M %p') %> - <%= @shift.end_time.strftime('%I:%M %p') %></p>
</div>

<p>Please make sure to arrive on time.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
VardiyaPro Team</p>
